        <mxCell id="GG1ei2N0N4fxY809Vq1g-68" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=14;" value="&amp;nbsp;failover , &lt;b&gt;active passive (needs to be discussed)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;thead&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;th&gt;Point&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CDN&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GSLB&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/thead&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Full form&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Content Delivery Network&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Global Server Load Balancing&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Main purpose&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Deliver content faster from nearest edge/cache&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Route users to the best data center/region&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Works mainly at&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Edge caching layer&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;DNS / global traffic routing layer&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Best for&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Images, JS, CSS, videos, static files, cacheable APIs&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Multi-region apps, active-active DC,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Users / Clients&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; |&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; v&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Global DNS / GSLB&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; |&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; +-------------------------------+&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; |&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;|&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; v&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;v&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Primary Region / DC-1&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;DR Region / DC-2&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Mumbai / Pune&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Hyderabad / Singapore&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; |&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;|&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; v&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;v&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;API Gateway / App Gateway&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; API Gateway / App Gateway&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; |&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;|&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; v&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;v&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Microservices&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Microservices&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; |&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;|&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; v&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;v&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;DB / Cache / Queue / Storage&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; DB / Cache / Queue / Storage&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Stores/caches content?&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Yes&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;No&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Sends user to nearest content server?&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Yes&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Yes, but mainly by routing to region/DC&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Handles failover?&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Yes, for cached content and some origins&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Yes, core purpose&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Protects origin load?&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Yes, by caching&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Indirectly, by distributing traffic&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Example services&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;CloudFront, Cloudflare CDN, Azure CDN, Akamai&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;Azure Traffic Manager, AWS Route 53 latency routing, F5 DNS/GTM, NS1&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Used between&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;User and origin/app/storage&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;User DNS and multiple regions/DCs&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;Simple meaning&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;“Serve content faster”&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;“Send user to the right region/DC”&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="400" width="580" x="1340" y="7760" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
